data.description: Great house in great community. Don't miss out on this updated all brick beauty located in a quiet neighborhood close to NAS Jax, shopping and I-295. The home has been re-plumbed, kitchen is updated with newer, countertops and cabinets overlooking the large fully fenced backyard perfect for pets and entertaining. The open patio is perfect for a grilling on summer evenings. LVP water proof flooring through out the entire home, newer windows. Split floor plan with a nice size master suite, master bath has been updated to include a walk-in shower. Inside laundry and plenty of windows complete this Westside charmer. Perfect Home or Investment property. NEW A/C
